  <h2>7. Web Beacons and Similar Technologies</h2>
  <p>
    In addition to cookies, we may use other similar technologies such as:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Web Beacons:</strong> Small images embedded in web pages or emails that help us track whether a page or email has been viewed.</li>
    <li><strong>Pixel Tags:</strong> Similar to web beacons, used to track user behavior and measure the effectiveness of our communications.</li>
    <li><strong>Local Storage:</strong> Data stored locally in your browser for enhanced functionality.</li>
    <li><strong>Session Storage:</strong> Temporary data stored for a single session.</li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    These technologies work similarly to cookies and are subject to the same privacy considerations outlined in our <a href="/legal/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a>.
  </p>

